{"tid":1786192,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"平均嚟講，黃店比藍店好食得多","createTime":"2019-12-17T03:24:42.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-17T03:33:10.000Z","uid":48234,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"b4186febf99bb5dea1a1a2c4dc543f456165313d","tid":1786192,"uid":48234,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-17T03:24:42.000Z","msg":"藍店求求其其亂鳩咁嚟就係人都知<br />\n連鎖店甚至連基本衛生都唔掂<br />\n黃店大多數食物質素真係比較好<br />\n<br />\n當然一定有啲個別嘅黃店做得唔夠好<br />\n俾人批評嘅黃店，要好好反省，或者搵返個有料嘅人幫手<br />\n<br />\n雖然話應該搞黃色經濟圈而唔只飲食<br />\n但飲食呢part的確係黃色經濟圈最重要嗰part<br />\n只要質素拋離藍店更遠，就算深藍都會被迫幫襯黃店<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ea7a8e35a852ff9b08e7494bf4dbf5cb90b67b85","tid":1786192,"uid":291309,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-17T03:26:31.000Z","msg":"中資係香港已成市場毒藥！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1786028\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1786028</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"2724ddbb46723d304f00c2163cbd4d80fc71ba97","tid":1786192,"uid":48234,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ea7a8e35a852ff9b08e7494bf4dbf5cb90b67b85","tid":1786192,"uid":291309,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-17T03:26:31.000Z","msg":"中資係香港已成市場毒藥！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1786028\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1786028</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-17T03:33:10.000Z","msg":"所以要抵制蚑資<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}